Invocation Name: tyro tarot
des: Do you have a burning question? Pull a Tarot card for Spiritual guidance. Say, “Alexa, draw a tarot card for me” and Alexa will let you know what card you got and what it means to you. Get Insights into your love life, career, finances, destiny, life path, and relationships with friends and family. Need more clarification? Ask Alexa to draw as many cards as you want!
